Package com.genesyslab.platform.configuration.protocol.runtime.channel

This package is used internally by the protocol. External usage is not supported. Classes from this package can be changed or even removed at any time.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AesUtil  
    CharDelimitersV6  
    CharDelimitersV7  
    ConfSerializer
    Base serialization for logic for 'V7' and 'V6' configuration data packing formats.
    ConfSerializerV6
    Configuration Protocol data serializer for 'V6' packing format.
    This format is used for transportation of configuration brief objects, objects/accounts permissions information, configuration schema and localization data.
    ConfSerializerV7
    Configuration Protocol data serializer for 'V7' packing format.
    This format is used for transportation of configuration objects information.
